            <button class="faq-question">What is the payment procedure?</button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <div class="faq-answer-content">
                You pay after you pass. We pride ourselves in our efficiency, hence the guarantee.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">What if I don't achieve my target score?</button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <div class="faq-answer-content">
                We offer a score improvement guarantee. If you don't reach your target score, you can retake the exam at no additional cost.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="faq-item">
            <button class="faq-question">Do you help with university applications?</button>
            <div class="faq-answer">
              <div class="faq-answer-content">
                Absolutely! We provide complete application support including university selection, SOP/essay writing, and visa interview preparation.
              </div>
